choices.text:
Put together a healthy meal plan for me for today presuming no dietary restrictions.
Breakfast: 1 whole grain toast with peanut butter and banana slices, black coffee or tea.
Lunch: Salad with mixed greens, chopped carrots, cucumbers, tomatoes, grilled chicken breast (or any other protein of your choice), balsamic vinegar and olive oil dressing. Fruit of your choice for dessert.
Dinner: Grilled or roasted salmon fillet with seasonings of your choice, steamed rice or quinoa, grilled asparagus or any other vegetable of your choice. Water or unsweetened herbal tea to drink.
